# Brief explanation

##### Given a number, evaluate if it's a palindrome number
##### [Palindrome number link](https://leetcode.com/problems/palindrome-number/)

I've created a reference for the numbers that are the answer for past numbers, and kept record for future validation and result presentation, by using a map that holds the index of the number that combined, result in the target. 

Evaluated submission

/**
 * @param {number} x
 * @return {boolean}
 */
var isPalindrome = function(x) {
    let i = 0;
    const jDoubt = `${x}`.length 
    while(i <= (jDoubt / 2)) {
        if(`${x}`[i] != `${x}`[jDoubt - (i+1)]) {
            return false
        }
        i++;
    }

    return true
};
